## Special note on Lindera + IPADIC (形態素解析辞書)

`lindera-ipadic` embeds the **IPADIC** morphological analyzer dictionary,
which is derived from MeCab IPADIC (originally produced at Nara Institute of
Science and Technology). The IPADIC is distributed under a BSD-3-Clause-style
license. Its full notice is preserved in this file via the `lindera-ipadic` crate.

